Title: Pick the better poem
Description: Given 2 poems on the same topic, decide which one is more creative and interesting
Input.title: Thinking of You
Input.poem_1:
Measure of our life. if we can find.
A better place to ease our minds.
I'm not the one to blame.
Though my thoughts make me go insane.
And the insanity of my nihilism.
Won't allow me to explore my pain.
Tears of joy are behind me
Even when I hear your name.
Input.poem_2:
I am thinking of you
This is nothing new
I sit there and stew
Over nothing else but you
